'''Ministry of Culture and National Heritage of the Republic of Poland''' ({{lang-pl|Ministerstwo Kultury i Dziedzictwa Narodowego}}) was formed on 31 October 2005, from transformation of ''Ministry of Culture of the Republic of Poland''.
The ministry is concerned with various aspects of [[Polish culture]].
The ministry can trace its history to 1944.
Current minister is [[Bogdan Zdrojewski]].
